One is, you're
mentioning Europe,

00:48:48.310 --> 00:48:50.160
United States, and China.

00:48:50.160 --> 00:48:54.060
How about other countries, maybe
in the developing or emerging

00:48:54.060 --> 00:48:57.770
nations, either because of
the access to technology,

00:48:57.770 --> 00:49:00.370
or because their
economical situation?

00:49:00.370 --> 00:49:01.860
And the second
question would be,

00:49:01.860 --> 00:49:06.590
how about the disparity between
any given society between those

00:49:06.590 --> 00:49:09.600
that have a lot and those that
have little in the present?

00:49:09.600 --> 00:49:12.565
Is it going to be different
in the next economic system

00:49:12.565 --> 00:49:13.315
that you envision?

